source: The Lickey Incline near Bromsgrove is the steepest railway incline in the UK. Unfortunately for you, you're running a passenger service to Birmingham New Street and the winter chill has had plenty of time to freeze up the rails. Prove you're a master of traction and defy the weather to get your Class 170 moving!
Translation: 布罗姆斯格罗夫附近的利基斜坡是英国最陡峭的铁路坡道。不幸的是，你正驾驶列车开往伯明翰新街站，而冬日的严寒早已将铁轨冻得结冰。展现你高超的牵引技术，克服恶劣天气，让你的170型机车顺利起步吧！

source: The morning had been passing so well! A Class 170 train has broken down in a tunnel at Birmingham New Street and has already caused a passenger service bound for Nottingham to be rerouted. You are the only driver terminating at Birmingham that is qualified to drive the Class 170, so you have been asked to help out with unblocking the track before your shift is over.
Translation: 上午一切都很顺利！一列170型列车在伯明翰新街车站的隧道里抛锚了，导致一趟开往诺丁汉的客运列车不得不改道。你是唯一一位有资格驾驶170型列车且终点站设在伯明翰的司机，所以被安排在下班前帮忙疏通轨道。

source: The signaller is calling. Use the radio to answer
Translation: 信号员正在呼叫。请使用无线电应答。

source: The track near Bromsgrove contains the tallest railway incline in the UK! Unfortunately for you, you're running a passenger service to Birmingham New Street and the snow has had plenty of time to freeze up the rails. Prove you're a master of traction and defy the weather to get your Class 170 moving!
Translation: 布罗姆斯格罗夫附近的铁轨拥有英国最高的铁路坡度！不幸的是，你正驾驶列车开往伯明翰新街站，积雪已经冻结了铁轨。展现你高超的牵引技术，克服恶劣天气，让你的170型机车重新出发吧！

source: The train is now ready to move. Set the Reverser to the Forward position.

source: There's no time to waste! We've already had to reroute several trains to avoid the stuck one. Head back to your train and get that Class 170 out of there.
Translation: 时间紧迫！我们已经不得不改道好几趟列车来避开那辆抛锚的列车。赶紧回到你的列车上，把那辆170型列车弄出来。

source: These guard panels are used to operate the train doors. Typically a conductor would operate this separately from the driver. Make sure the doors are closed, then sit back down in the Driver's Seat and we can get the train moving.
Translation: 这些防护面板用于操作列车车门。通常情况下，列车员会独立于驾驶员操作这些面板。请确保车门已关闭，然后回到驾驶座上，我们就可以启动列车了。
